# Project 1: College Resource Management System

## Problem Statement
In many colleges, students have to search in different places for notes, previous question papers, announcements, and other study materials. This process is time-consuming and inefficient.

## Objective
The objective of this project is to provide a centralized platform where students can easily access all college resources. An AI chatbot is integrated to answer common student queries.

## System Architecture / Workflow

```
Student
   │
   ▼
React Frontend
   │
   ▼
Node.js + Express.js
   │
   ▼
MongoDB Database
   │
   ▼
AI Chatbot
```

## Modules

- User Authentication (JWT)
- Resource Management
- AI Chatbot
- User Dashboard

## Results & Benefits

- Centralized access to study materials
- Reduced search time
- Secure authentication
- Quick responses through AI chatbot

## Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| React.js | Frontend |
| Node.js | Backend |
| Express.js | API Development |
| MongoDB | Database |
| JWT | Authentication |
| JavaScript | Programming Language |

