# Project 2: Cyberbullying Detection System

## Problem Statement
Detecting abusive and harmful comments manually on social media is difficult due to the large volume of user-generated content.

## Objective
To automatically identify cyberbullying comments using Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning.

## System Architecture / Workflow

```
Dataset
   │
   ▼
Text Preprocessing
   │
   ▼
Feature Extraction
   │
   ▼
Machine Learning Model
   │
   ▼
Prediction
```

## Modules

- Data Collection
- Text Preprocessing
- Feature Extraction
- Model Training
- Prediction

## Results & Benefits

- Achieved 88% prediction accuracy
- Faster detection of harmful content
- Supports safer online communication

## Technologies Used

| Technology | Purpose |
|------------|---------|
| Python | Programming |
| Scikit-learn | Machine Learning |
| Pandas | Data Processing |
| NumPy | Numerical Computing |
| NLP | Text Processing |

